theorem
    for V being non empty RLSStruct, M,N being Subset of V, r being Real st
 M c= N holds r*M c= r*N by Lm6;

theorem
    for V being non empty LoopStr, M being empty Subset of V,
 N being Subset of V holds M + N = {} by Lm8;

